_sText:
My first finished de_ map. It taught me a lot about the layout of maps and playtesting it on a server with real people really helped to balance it out.

This map was playtested by people in the GpX clan back in early 2006, and the almighty Toku from TeamLogitech.fi had a go on it. Thanks Toku, it made my day :)

Oh and by the way, the objective is to destroy the crates as Terrorists, and to defend those precious crates as CT.
